sentences: Melvin Seals (born 1953 in San Francisco, California) is an American musician, best known as a longtime member of the Jerry Garcia Band.
In 1980 Melvin Seals joined the Jerry Garcia Band and remained a member until Jerry Garcia's death in 1995.

After Garcia and Kahn's deaths in 1995 and 1996 respectively, Seals formed JGB which he performs with to this day.
On July 30, 2004, Seals was the first Jerry Garcia Band member to headline an outdoor music and camping festival named in honor of Jerry Garcia, called Grateful Garcia Gathering.
Jerry Garcia Band drummer David Kemper joined Melvin Seals & JGB in 2007.
In 2005 Seals released his first solo CD entitled Melting Pot.
